subSubSection.paragraph:
This subspecies group extends over the entire Palaearctic and comprises forms quite well differentiated in coloration and proportions (for rufipectus see above).
P. ater abietum
in central Europe must be acknowledged (
Eck 1984
;
Roselaar 1995
;
Corbet 2004
).

